 About Pod

 Pod is an X-windows interface to the
 Quipu  based  X.500  directory  service. It 
 allows users to search  through and extract
 information  from   a  worldwide  database.
 
 The following  is  a  brief guide to
 Pod's  functionality.  More  detailed  help
 will  be  displayed  automatically  as  you
 experiment.

 Button      Action

 <List>      List entries closest to the
             'Current Directory Position.'

 <Search>    Search for entries with value
             entered in 'Search' dialog box.

 <History>   List entries that have been
 	     visited before.

